      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CYCLONE SEBAS (8) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by a neck at Taree Super Track in a handy 17.51 beating Calla Naughty. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. The hardest to beat again. ICE ON FIRE (2) goes very well over this track and trip including five wins. Below best last time at Grafton (20.03) in a NG, finishing a 4.5 lengths fourth. Among the main chances. BLUE CHANELLE (1) missed the frame last time when sixth (30.49) at this track but prior to that had two placings in a row. Solid record at the distance winning six races. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Key player if finds best. STYLISH ROBBO (5) generally performs well over this distance.",
